### 5. Pipeline Registration (SUPPORTED_TASKS Mapping)

**Location:** Lines 3096-3390 in pipelines.js

The `SUPPORTED_TASKS` constant is a frozen object mapping task names to their configurations:

```javascript
const SUPPORTED_TASKS = Object.freeze({
    "text-classification": {
        "tokenizer": AutoTokenizer,
        "pipeline": TextClassificationPipeline,
        "model": AutoModelForSequenceClassification,
        "default": {
            "model": "Xenova/distilbert-base-uncased-finetuned-sst-2-english",
        },
        "type": "text",
    },

    // ... more entries ...

    "image-to-text": {
        "tokenizer": AutoTokenizer,
        "pipeline": ImageToTextPipeline,
        "model": AutoModelForVision2Seq,
        "processor": AutoProcessor,
        "default": {
            "model": "Xenova/vit-gpt2-image-captioning",
        },
        "type": "multimodal",
    },

    "zero-shot-image-classification": {
        "tokenizer": AutoTokenizer,
        "pipeline": ZeroShotImageClassificationPipeline,
        "model": AutoModel,
        "processor": AutoProcessor,
        "default": {
            "model": "Xenova/clip-vit-base-patch32",
        },
        "type": "multimodal",
    },

    "document-question-answering": {
        "tokenizer": AutoTokenizer,
        "pipeline": DocumentQuestionAnsweringPipeline,
        "model": AutoModelForDocumentQuestionAnswering,
        "processor": AutoProcessor,
        "default": {
            "model": "Xenova/donut-base-finetuned-docvqa",
        },
        "type": "multimodal",
    },

    // ... 20+ more entries ...
})
```

**Registration Entry Structure:**
- `"tokenizer"` - Auto tokenizer class (optional, for text-based tasks)
- `"pipeline"` - The pipeline class to instantiate
- `"model"` - Auto model class(es) - can be a single class or array of classes
- `"processor"` - Auto processor class (optional, for multimodal/audio/image tasks)
- `"default"` - Default model ID to use if none specified
- `"type"` - Task type category: "text", "audio", "image", "multimodal"

**Task Aliases:** Lines 3394-3403

