## Context

Transformers.js currently supports `image-to-text` (image captioning, using `AutoModelForVision2Seq`) but has no pipeline for models that take **both** an image and a text prompt to produce generated text (e.g. LLaVA, SmolVLM, Qwen2-VL, PaliGemma). The `AutoModelForImageTextToText` model class already exists in `src/models.js` (line 8736) and maps to 11 concrete model implementations. This plan adds the missing pipeline to expose those models via the standard `pipeline()` factory, following every existing pattern exactly.

